"{\"uid\": \"athens-times.com-volunteer-for-the-olympics-games-found-dead-in-her-apartment-arrested-as-a-suspect-her-partner\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Athens Times  -  A woman who volunteered in Paris was found in her apartment, with the police arresting her partner as a suspect in the murder.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9991047505197582, \"rank\": 0.0008772283756049109, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999446010531635, \"rank\": 5.5402016100394275e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An unpleasant news brings to light the French \\\"leparisien\\\" as according to her report, a young volunteer at the Olympic Games was found dead inside her apartment, the day after the Olympic Games ended in Paris.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8502417046010806, \"rank\": 0.1742923121514633, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999446010531635, \"rank\": 5.5402016100394275e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically, the victim's mother had reported the disappearance of her 21-year-old daughter, with the police following investigations tracking the unfortunate girl dead in her apartment.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The body had haematoma on the left side of the head and a neck wound, with the body being transferred to the Paris Medical Institute, where it will undergo an autopsy-death in the following period.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999446010531635, \"rank\": 5.5402016100394275e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, the authorities went on to arrest her partner, as he through a message told his relatives that he was doing something \\\"foolish\\\".\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During his arrest the suspect was drunk and was in a coma.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the report states, he tried to end his life by taking drugs.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it makes sense after his arrest, this man will be called to an apology in order to give more details about the case.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For now no more details have been given to the public than the brutal murder.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athens Times  News about Greece and the World.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9991047505197582, \"rank\": 0.0008772283756049109, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.96963714867445